.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, november, july, june, april
House: cottage, farmhouse, tower, gothic-revival, ranch-style
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: decembermaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
5 different pets are kept: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. the cottage house is the person who's birthday is in july
2. the swedish house is the owner of the dog
3. the farmhouse house is the person drinking tea
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june
5. the person who's birthday is in november is the person drinking coffee
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the owner of the bird
7. the person who's birthday is in april is the dunhill-smoker
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the gothic-revival house is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the cat
11. the owner of the horses is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the decembermaster-smoker is the person drinking beer
13. the tower house is the prince-smoker
14. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Birthday		|    april	|     december	|      july	|     november	|     june	|
| House	|   gothic-revival	|    farmhouse	|    cottage	|    tower	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     cat	|    horse	|     bird	|     fish	|      dog	|
| Beverage	|    water	|     tea	|     milk	|    coffee	|      beer	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   decembermaster	|
